              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Time of flight with path length of 28.32+-0.05",
                " meters. ARMCO natural iron filter, 20.32-cm thick,",
                " used to reduce background. Boron-carbide filter used",
                " to eliminate overlap low energy neutrons, lead filter",
                " reduced soft x-rays. Two runs made- enriched Fe-56",
                " sample cycled in and out of beam to determine cross",
                " section, 0.0762-cm natural Fe sample used to determine",
                " neutron energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
